&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16620282" author="brunoz" created="Wed, 19 Sep 2018 08:23:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks but when you import such exported using CQL.json(String), you have :&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Error decoding JSON value for value: Value &apos;&apos; is not a valid blob representation: String representation of blob is missing 0x prefix: &lt;br/&gt;
 com.datastax.driver.core.exceptions.InvalidQueryException: Error decoding JSON value for value: Value &apos;&apos; is not a valid blob representation: String representation of blob is missing 0x prefix: &lt;br/&gt;
